Integrated Pump Technology was established as the official southern Africa distributor for the well-respected Grindex range of electrical submersible pump. Today the company has grown its offering to include Italian manufactured Faggiolati pumps. Both are Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) brands with established global footprints. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 8 2018. It will be published online on the 12th September 2018. You can read the full digital magazine here or subscribe here to receive a print copy